e: ￹`O~ `ka~`seneng~`an~ `ita~ `ko~ `nika~ `tadamaan~ `no~ `Tapang~ `ita~.￺We are proud of the greatness of our Lord.￻上帝的偉大(全能)是我們的光榮(主的至高無尚令我們敬畏)
￹`Pa~`seneng~ / `pa~`sngi~ `kita~ `to~ `fana'~ `ita~￺We boast of our knowledge.￻我們誇耀我們的智慧
￹`Sa~`wadaw~ `ko~ `misa~`pasene~`senengay~ `a~ `sowal~.￺Stop (your) boastful word.￻停止你誇大的言語，不要再講自誇的話
￹`Ma~`seneng~ `kako~.￺1. I feel threatened by his ability.  2. I feel panic from heights.￻1. 我被他的能力所脅迫  2. 從高處往下看有畏懼感
d.f: ￹￺displayed * something to be proud of￻驕傲，誇示，炫耀，光榮，對某東西感得意
